# Glitch deploy workflow

## Source of truth

- All edits happen in `D:\click-blue\trading\glitch-platform\ninjatrader\Glitch`.
- Never edit, rename, move, or delete files directly under `C:\Users\alan\Documents\NinjaTrader 8\bin\Custom`.

## Deploy scope

- Live AddOn deploys are full-folder only.
- Always copy the entire `D:\click-blue\trading\glitch-platform\ninjatrader\Glitch\AddOns\GlitchAddOn` tree to `C:\Users\alan\Documents\NinjaTrader 8\bin\Custom\AddOns\GlitchAddOn`.
- Never cherry-pick individual AddOn files for live deploy.
- Indicator and Strategy deploys still require explicit user request and separate intent confirmation.

## Workflow

- Finish the patch in the workspace first.
- Validate workspace files first.
- Run the approved deploy script once with the complete recursive `GlitchAddOn` file list.
- Report the copy map in the handoff.
